ia-label="Wikipedia" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=ca17fb9b396adde32ab23380c291ca97b425eb707e02f13e0a4ab640e0ff6644JmltdHM9MTc4MTMwODgwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=180e2851-b9d1-65ae-0ad1-3d3cb8f0647c&amp;psq=electricidad&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lcy53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvRWxlY3RyaWNpZGFk&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5204.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./conclusion_files/ODF(1).INhCOd4qElPoejfhZYl17A" height="32" width="32" alt="Icono de web global" class="rms_img" data-bm="56"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">Wikipedia</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://es.wikipedia.org › wiki › Electricidad</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=ca17fb9b396adde32ab23380c291ca97b425eb707e02f13e0a4ab640e0ff6644JmltdHM9MTc4MTMwODgwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=180e2851-b9d1-65ae-0ad1-3d3cb8f0647c&amp;psq=electricidad&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lcy53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvRWxlY3RyaWNpZGFk&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5204.2">Electricidad - Wikipedia, la enciclopedia libre</a></h2><div class="b_caption"></div><div id="5468" class="b_wikiGbMod"><a class="b_wikiGbModHero" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=8bec94cc87031a8104141baa5105c46da66e58b897c09ed0638082a73d75d766JmltdHM9MTc4MTMwODgwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=180e2851-b9d1-65ae-0ad1-3d3cb8f0647c&amp;psq=electricidad&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lcy53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvRWxlY3RyaWNpZGFkI0hlcm9TZWN0aW9u&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5470.1">La electricidad (del griego ήλεκτρον élektron, cuyo significado es ‘ámbar’) ​ es el conjunto de fenómenos físicos relacionados con la presencia y flujo de carga eléctricas. Se manifiesta en una gran variedad de fenómenos como los rayos, la electricidad estática, la inducción …</a><div class="b_wikiGbModCards"><div><div id="b_acf_tc_19871F3" class="b_acf_card b_wikiGbModCard acf_t_c acf_padding b_acf_bckgnd" data-k="5866" data-appns="SERP" link=""><a title="" class="b_acf_card_link" target="_blank" tabindex="0" aria-label="Usos" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=974c2f88cbb08cd3f1c1bc669cdf091cc61d8f54de06ae8b66b97ae29aa70420JmltdHM9MTc4MTMwODgwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=180e2851-b9d1-65ae-0ad1-3d3cb8f0647c&amp;psq=electricidad&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lcy53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvRWxlY3RyaWNpZGFkI1Vzb3M&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5472.1"></a><div class="acf_t_c_content "><div class="acf_t_c_inner"><div class="acf_t_c_title_cont"><div style="-webkit-line-clamp: 1; line-clamp: 1;" class="acf_t_c_title" role="heading" aria-level="2">Usos</div><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_container"><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_icon"><svg id="acfchevronicon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.40617 3.20041C6.10264 3.48226 6.08506 3.95681 6.36691 4.26034L9.89303 8L6.36691 11.7397C6.08506 12.0432 6.10264 12.5177 6.40617 12.7996C6.7097 13.0815 7.18425 13.0639 7.4661 12.7603L11.4661 8.51034C11.7333 8.22258 11.7333 7.77743 11.4661 7.48966L7.4661 3.23966C7.18425 2.93613 6.7097 2.91856 6.40617 3.20041Z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="-webkit-line-clamp: 6; line-clamp: 6; overflow:hidden;" class="acf_t_c_body">La electricidad se usa para generar: <br>• luz, mediante bombillas en lámparas y otros objetos lumínicos.<br>• Calor, aprovechando el efecto Joule.<br>• Movimiento, mediante motores que transforman la energía eléctrica en …<br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="b_bimgSetrcw"><div class="bimgclgsw19113"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:310px;height:198px;"><a title="Ver detalles" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Lightning3.jpg/250px-Lightning3.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.820613d2853704a283389078697c87f9&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Lightning3.jpg/250px-Lightning3.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5471.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="198" width="310" data-src-hq="https://thf.bing.com/th/id/ODL.820613d2853704a283389078697c87f9?w=310&amp;h=198&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=ffff14&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb32A238723" class="rms_img" src="./conclusion_files/ODL.820613d2853704a283389078697c87f9" loading="lazy" data-bm="57"></a></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="b_bimgSetrcw"><div class="bimgclgsw1919"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:206px;height:198px;"><a title="Ver detalles" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/Cargas_electricas.png/250px-Cargas_electricas.png&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.33af93934950d39769fc59525abdc91b&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/Cargas_electricas.png/250px-Cargas_electricas.png" h="ID=SERP,5474.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="198" width="206" data-src-hq="https://thf.bing.com/th/id/ODL.33af93934950d39769fc59525abdc91b?w=206&amp;h=198&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=fffffc&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb427709E2F" class="rms_img" src="./conclusion_files/ODL.33af93934950d39769fc59525abdc91b" loading="lazy" data-bm="58"></a></div></div><div class="bimgclgsw15913"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:102px;height:98px;"><a title="Ver detalles" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Atomo_di_rame.svg/250px-Atomo_di_rame.